				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1151095#post-2253808</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1151095/scp-2760#post-2253808</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2015 20:58:29 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Accelerando</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1599414</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm not quite sure, I've had the idea in my sandbox for a long time. I originally wanted only one airdancer that behaved like a dragon, but I guess making the airdancer a dragon itself was more appealing. I also wanted to emphasize how it was the only one of its kind, but a dragon pair made more sense to me for some reason.</p> 
				 	]]>
