					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1151095#post-2253797</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1151095/scp-2760#post-2253797</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2015 20:39:07 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>scants</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2015916</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Just imagine if they found a giant bouncy house dealership. Given, those are few and far between, but think about the massacre&#8230;</p> <p><em>shudders</em></p> <p>Anyway, loved the article, if just for the final log. But I have to know: how did you come up with this idea? It's so novel that even those new cabbage-pumpkin-carrot lattes couldn't compete with it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
